snippet.title: 배고픈 원시인 3차 트레일러(Hungry Caveman third trailer)
snippet.description:
레인보우스튜디오 신작!
배고픈원시인 리메이크(원작은 2019년작) 3차 트레일러 영상입니다.
오늘도 즐거운 하루되세요.

스팀 주소 : https://store.steampowered.com/app/2166250
찜하기, 팔로우는 감사합니다!

Rainbow Studio's new game!
The Hungry Caveman Remake (originally in 2019)
This is the third trailer video.
Have a great day today.

Steam Link : https://store.steampowered.com/app/2166250
Thank you for the wishlist, follow!
